  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK527">
<l>kākkai karavā karaintuṇṇu mākkamu</l>
<l>maṉṉanī rārkkē yuḷa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The crows do not conceal (their prey), but will call out for others (to share with them) while they eat it; wealth will be with those who show a similar disposition (towards their relatives).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
